goes into hibernation.

01:18:46.756 --> 01:18:52.093
But that February we had
this unseasonable warm,

01:18:52.095 --> 01:18:54.662
and the temperatures
got up to about 70.

01:18:54.664 --> 01:18:57.832
And everyone's outside
in their t-shirts,

01:18:57.834 --> 01:19:03.003
and all of sudden boxo
comes out of hibernation.

01:19:03.005 --> 01:19:05.806
And Todd's out there
taking him for walks,

01:19:05.808 --> 01:19:08.075
and I'm jealous.

01:19:08.077 --> 01:19:10.277
But then sun goes away.

01:19:11.379 --> 01:19:14.982
The warm spell ends
and it's winter again.

01:19:14.984 --> 01:19:18.185
Boxo can't go back
into hibernation.

01:19:18.187 --> 01:19:21.255
So after a few days,
he dies.

